author: Connor Creates
description:
my alter ego Connor Destroys really came out at the end lol

This was a really fun challenge to try and do blacksmithing at home without spending any money! I definitely learned lots, and I have a new appreciation for all the vikings/blacksmiths out there!

Come say hi on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/itsconnorcreates
And subscribe here on YT: youtube.com/@itsConnorCreates

thanks for watching this video, I appreciate your support! :) and special thank you to all those who purchased a hat from my first ever merch drop!

#forging #blacksmith #knifeforging #diyprojects #vikings
title: I Did Expensive Knife Forging for FREE
